    "This dovetails with recent developments in the field testifying that small language models are often sufficiently powerful and far more economical in agentic systems [14,15].",
    "(2) We develop a novel reward training design that goes beyond accuracy.",
    "The resulting Orchestrator is trained end-to-end to balance task outcome correctness, efficiency in cost and latency, and alignment with user cost and tool preferences.",
    "(3) We demonstrate that Orchestrator trained by ToolOrchestra achieves state-of-the-art performance on challenging reasoning benchmarks, surpassing frontier models while using only a fraction of their compute and wall-clock time, and that it generalizes robustly to unseen tasks and tools.",
